Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.65,0:01:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分开了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.63,0:01:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座山因为被邪恶帝皇\N多恶达支配了的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连彩虹的颜色也变成了黑白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.80,0:01:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、火美子和武一郎师傅\N一边与多恶达的魔神战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.81,0:01:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于上到了第三界层了\N原本第三界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.32,0:01:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由支配寒冷的极寒之剑\N与支配炎热的灼热之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令这处的气温刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.56,0:02:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是多恶达用灼热之剑\N换了极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.94,0:02:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令第三界层变成了个\N热得不得了的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.80,0:02:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要令这个世界恢复原本的气温\N便一定要找出极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.03,0:02:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于知道了\N它竟在第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.64,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和龙神丸、火美子、师傅\N分离上到了第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五话\N唤醒吧!火龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.30,0:03:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了多恶达大人\N是不会就此算数的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.30,0:03:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢呢\N火美子和百人仙人没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,你认为怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没可能会没问题吧?\N我的立场到底会变成怎样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从刚才起\N便一直在自言自语什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔!\N回来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,只有你一人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.67,0:03:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡上了第四界层啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?第四界层?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说一定会\N把极寒之剑带回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了!不行了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生\N不是不行了,是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才是不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,百人仙人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了?怎么回事?\N我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.73,0:03:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所也所也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢欺骗我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?什么意思?古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.90,0:04:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丢脸了,古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古…古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?一定要处理你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷…\N这里便是第四界层吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和第三界层完全相反呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.10,0:04:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点找出极寒之剑\N会死在这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!龙神丸呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,是用尽了能量吗?\N要怎样才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.47,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,去找火龙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火龙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.00,0:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火龙?我明白了\N总之找到火龙便可以了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.87,0:05:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天定会捉到你\N让你知道抵抗是没有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.48,0:05:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会让你接近洞穴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!小蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.89,0:06:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪珠!去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来,小蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.48,0:06:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无用的反抗!无用的反抗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了,停啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已说了那是无用的反抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边有没有什么事发生?\N东杰何狄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,多多高麾大人\N这么精神真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢!我收到联络\N渡已上了这个第四界层了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是玩的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是刚才的家伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东杰何狄,我们在此收拾渡\N天下便是我们的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.90,0:07:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时我们\N便可以支配更高的界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.70,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以成为\N多恶达大人的左右手,快追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.82,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,我现在立刻开始追击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看来不像是\N多恶达的手下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.15,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雪,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个,是名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找极寒之剑\N从第三界层来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极寒之剑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在在找火龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火龙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的背叛者\N知道厉害了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.22,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有背叛啊,所也所也\N请你多给我一次机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦!\N现在的你可以做到什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你一个好消息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.08,0:08:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在残酷大人、残恶鸟大人\N残豹大人快来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔…魔界三兄弟吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.50,0:09:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,是多恶达大人\N命令他们来杀了你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开门啊!竟困我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.91,0:09:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为在下是谁啊?\N在下是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河马啊!\N是啊!喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拿到那家伙的钥匙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去取回来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以离开这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不早说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.06,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又没有问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,快去取吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.10,0:09:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法,开锁之术\N出门之前不要忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.00,0:09:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.50,0:09:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要静静的去啊,静静的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[残豹]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[残恶鸟]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[残酷]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的故乡\N高千高千市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.00,0:11:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高千高千市?\N火龙在这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里怎么了?大家也冰封了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样的?\N这是突然发生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天忽然有团黑雾\N来到这里上空…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.62,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因拿着爷爷给我的遗物\N火龙的鳞片才能得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火龙的鳞片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.20,0:11:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在龙之洞穴的火龙\N是火炎之龙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿着这鳞片\N便不会冰封了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它住在龙之洞穴吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然火龙也许能\N令这市镇恢复原状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.84,0:12:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是支配着这里的\N东杰何狄阻挡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我不能接近洞穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,去龙之洞穴吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.33,0:12:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令市镇恢复原状\N也许会知道极寒之剑在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.60,0:12:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残…残酷将军,请原谅我\N请你给多一次机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.40,0:12:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!以为有事\N可以求得动残兄弟大人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.35,0:12:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥,不如把这背叛者\N烧了来吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊,会吃坏肚子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥,我已很腻了\N还是快杀了他走人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.19,0:12:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所也所也\N够了,快了结他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿矛来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,你觉悟吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请停手\N所也所也,再给多一次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.68,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所也所也\N这家伙的命暂时交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还有点利用价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.42,0:13:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下去收拾他们\N你在这里等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,趁现在快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要救鸟先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.74,0:13:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢\N可是不知道他被困在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鸟先生的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪边?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了!辛苦你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗?\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.83,0:14:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子\N你再用多次刚才的开锁术吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!鸟先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧,我现在来救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.10,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…是来救我的吗?\N为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊?\N我们不是同伴吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴啊!同伴啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同…同伴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你痛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.40,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这药是忍部一族\N代代相传的万能药啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂了这个的话\N不论什么伤也会很快复原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.93,0:14:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为何只有古拿玛一个\N要受这些苦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…因为我知道很多东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲也是什么也知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.01,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这药的制法\N也是父亲教我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有父亲的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪里?\N不知所踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不知所踪?\N怎会这样的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去了收拾多恶达\N但没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的另一半是我父亲拿着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?看来好像什么痛苦\N也没有的长大的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.07,0:15:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来也有这么痛苦的过去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受了伤的时候\N父亲也是这样子摸我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.32,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!\N今天眼睛特别多汗流出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.40,0:15:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样,你经常用笑脸\N来隐藏和父亲分离的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下最怕听这种事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.30,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子你放心吧\N在下一定会帮你找出你父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前\N你便当我是你的父亲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲\N是比你好很多的男人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,你暂时忍耐一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.12,0:16:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说客气话了\N走吧,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.32,0:16:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这里吗?\N如果是火龙住不是太冷了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但的确应该是这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条不是火龙而是冰龙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它向这边来了,快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无用的反抗也到此为止了\N渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.07,0:16:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是东杰何狄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.04,0:16:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火龙已被多恶达大人\N变成冰龙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无用的反抗呢\N辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.80,0:17:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.80,0:17:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,它已不能变回火龙了吗\N镇内的人也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是没办法\N只要除掉那金颈环便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.90,0:17:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是无用的反抗\N这是绝对不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.15,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗有分什么有用无用吗?\N战斗也有分战了也没改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…总之只有试试了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.86,0:17:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰龙\N把那傲慢的小鬼变成冰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有干了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.94,0:17:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已说了这是无用的反抗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.00,0:17:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再做无用的反抗了\N一起看渡被冰封吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了,龙神丸不能动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,火龙的鳞片!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.84,0:18:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.82,0:18:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会变冰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,把鳞片投出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.44,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.95,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,苏醒吧!火龙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!是机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.29,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了,这不是无用的反抗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么便用魔神决胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火龙\N请你令雪的市镇恢复原状吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火龙,谢谢你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼\N我要把你打得体无完肤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无用的反抗!无用的反抗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.28,0:20:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.12,0:20:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!\N渡,你做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做无用的反抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,用飞龙拳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞龙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.75,0:21:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无用的反抗啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.31,0:21:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,谢谢你从多恶达的咒缚中\N把我解放出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.60,0:21:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火龙,可以告诉我极寒之剑\N在哪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.00,0:21:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道极寒之剑在哪里\N但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.36,0:21:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,接着去北面的野野谷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.51,0:21:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有极寒之剑的线索的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野野谷?雪,你认识路吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.39,0:22:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.26,0:22:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可以带我去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.80,0:22:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.87,0:22:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!出发吧\N目的地是野野谷!


